#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Let's start with the `Fruit` entity.Create the `src/main/java/org/acme/hibernate/orm/panache/Fruit.java` file with the following content:"
msgstr "让我们从 `水果` 实体开始。创建包含以下内容的 `src/main/java/org/acme/hibernate/orm/panache/Fruit.java` 文件："

